## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

{% if framework == "astro" %}
- Node.js 18 or later
- npm, pnpm, or yarn
{% elif framework == "nextjs-static" %}
- Node.js 18 or later
- npm, pnpm, or yarn
{% elif framework == "hugo" %}
- Hugo extended v0.120 or later (`brew install hugo` / `winget install Hugo.Hugo.Extended`)
{% elif framework == "eleventy" %}
- Node.js 18 or later
- npm or yarn
{% endif %}

### Install and run

{% if framework == "astro" %}
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

The site starts at `http://localhost:4321`.
{% elif framework == "nextjs-static" %}
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

The site starts at `http://localhost:3000`.
{% elif framework == "hugo" %}
```bash
hugo server --buildDrafts
```

The site starts at `http://localhost:1313`. Live reload is included.
{% elif framework == "eleventy" %}
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

The site starts at `http://localhost:8080`.
{% endif %}

